Univariate Model

JAGS Model

model{
  prec.Sigma~dwish(Vsig[,],n)
  Sigma[1:n,1:n] <- inverse(prec.Sigma[,])
  
  mu[1:n]~dmnorm(mu0[],Vmu)
  
  for(i in 1:N){
    for(j in 1:n){
      X[i,j]~dnorm(Y[i,j],10000000)
      }
    Y[i,1:n]~dmnorm(mu[],prec.Sigma[,])
    }
  }
